name: MOE
description: What is the project about? : $MOE is the fuel for recording MOE on the blockchain. It is used when minting NFTs and also for voting in popularity contests. What makes your project unique? : Every time a MOE NFT is minted on the blockchain, all the used $MOE is burned. The scarcity of $MOE continues to increase regardless.
